Package com.skillstorm.hotel.models

Class Customers

java.lang.Object
com.skillstorm.hotel.models.Customers
@Entity public class Customers extends Object
This is the models class for the customers table in MySQL. It contains each of the variables within the customers table, with the correct annotations to denote their respective table properties.
Author:
Todd Foreman
